The paper deals with the construction of Service Oriented Architecture, which is a topic related to programming languages and software engineering. Therefore, cs.PL and cs.SE are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of trace semantics and equational theory, which are topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper presents a novel approach to establishing equivalence between service protocols, which is a topic related to logic in computer science (cs.LO).
